e what has been kept.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="area_gold" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #fff; font-family: Georgia; font-style: italic; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0;">Free deliveries and collections</span>[sf_button colour="blue" type="standard" size="standard" link="#" icon="ss-erase" dropshadow="no" extraclass="login_link"]<span style="color: #ffffff;">MORE DETAILS</span>[/sf_button]</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax]', 'How it works', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-04-01 11:34:10', '2014-04-01 11:34:10', '', 8, 'http://enclothed.dev/8-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
	(668, 6, '2014-04-07 14:21:41', '2014-04-07 14:21:41', '[spb_slider revslider_shortcode="how-it-works-slider" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" el_class="area2_left" width="1/2" el_position="first"]\n\n<img class="size-full aligncenter" alt="create_your_profile" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/create_your_profile.jpg" />\n\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" el_class="area2_right" width="1/2" el_position="last"]\n\n<img class="size-full line" alt="line" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/line.png" />\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Create your style profile</h2>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Simply tell us a bit about your style, size and preferences and our technology will turn that into a style profile that your stylist will then use to pick you great clothes.</p>\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_row wrap_type="content-width" row_bg_color="#f6f7f6" parallax_type="color" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" row_overlay_opacity="0" row_padding_vertical="30" row_margin_vertical="30" remove_element_spacing="no" el_class="area3" width="1/1" el_position="first last"] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" el_class="area3_left" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\n\n<img class="size-full line" alt="line" src="/wp-content/themes/dante-child/images/line.png" />\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">At your request</h2>\n<p style="text-align: left;">We are not a subscription service! We will only send you a box when you request one.</p>\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" el_class="area3_right hidden-xs" width="2/3" el_position="last"]\n<div class="order_a_box_wrapper">\n<p class="georgia_text georgia_text1 hidden-sm">Let us know if there’s anything specific you need</p>\n<p class="georgia_tex